
###Chrome
cd .config/google-chrome
mv Default temp
rm -rf Default
cp -R temp Default


###Thunderbird
go to .thunderbird and into the folder (only folder there, which has the profile) (in doubt check the thunderbird.ini file for path of the profile folder).
Once in the profile folder, erase the file .parentlock.

####Mozilla
change places.sqlite to some other name, than make a copy and call it places. sqlite
